Name: Staging
Description: This module will be used to validate material movement from staging area to Dispensing booth.

Description: This module will be used to Dispensed material which is to be issued to Production department.

Name: StageOut
Description: This module will be used stage out the Loose Material.

Name: ReturntoVendor
Destruction
Description: This module will be used destroy the rejected material.

Name: WeighingCalibration
Description: This module will be used to Calibrate the weighing balance as per the planner.

Name: Plant
Description: The master module will be used to create/update the Plant Master details in database. Different Plants in the organization will be mentioned here.

Name: Gate
Description: All inward stock movement starts, and all outward movement ends through Gate. Gate pass is generated at the gate which helps controlling vehicle movement inside a plant.

Name: Location
Description: The master module will be used to create/update the Location Master details in database. A barcode will be generated for Locations and will affix on the locations, this will provide a unique identification to each Location. User can take print out of Location barcode as well through this module.

Name: Cubicle
Description: Cubicles are generally closed areas under zone and are meant for specific activities. Many times, they may be restricted except few authorized users.

Name: Equipment
Description: Equipment that are required to perform various activities. For example, for weighing activity the weight machine or weighing scale is used. Similarly, computers, scanners, machineries etc. are equipment that are used in warehouse activities as catalyst or helper but they themselves are not consumed for production.

Name: Calendar
Description: This master will contain Calendar details which will define weekly off and Holiday for particular plant.

Name: HandlingUnit
Description: A Handling Unit is a physical unit consisting of packaging materials (load carriers/packing material) and the goods contained on/in it. A handling unit is always a combination of products and packaging materials.

Name: StandardWeightBox
Description: This master will contain Standard Weight Box details which are used while weighing calibration. With the help of this master, in this master Standard Weight Box Id will be maintain as unique id.

Name: StandardWeight
Description: This master will contain Standard Weight details which are used while weighing calibration. With the help of this master, in this master Standard weight Id will be maintain as unique Id.

Name: Department
Description: This master will contain Department details which will define department in Plants. With the help of this master will maintain department details.

Name: UnitOfMeasurement
Description: Unit of Measure (UoM) is a quantity used as a standard of measurement for the inventory. PMMS defines all standard units used in inventory and the conversion rates from one to another.

Name: Area
Description: This master will contain Area details which will define Area in Departments. With the help of this master will maintain area details.

Name: WeighingMachine
Description: This master will contain Weighing Machine details. With the help of this master, user will print barcode label for Weighing Machine to provide unique identification to each Weighing Machine at Store and will be able to update or delete the required Weighing Machine details.

Name: Checklist
Description: Checklist is used in various activities like vehicle inspection, material inspection, cubicle cleaning, line, clearance for Cubicle etc. Checklist will be created as per module will displayed in that specific module only.
